{"tid":2037280,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有必要講下 同我入黎! 咪撚再用支那字 咩咩打造 黑科技...屌你老母","createTime":"2020-05-27T01:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T12:36:08.000Z","uid":10788,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"482838d70eecd593d6d6a12eed2e62126dce35a0","tid":2037280,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:45:11.000Z","msg":"連登香港第一反共論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />竟然咁多手捉不知不覺用咗咁多支那字都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你自己口講都唔撚順口喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打造<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 製造,生產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(聽到唔知咩新聞 周柏豪話 多謝團體同一齊打造XXX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該用合作呢個字)<br />\n黑科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小三<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狐狸精,第三者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑材料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醜聞 痛腳 黑幕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炒作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />煲水新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (呢個真係好少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />....)<br />\n吸睛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搶眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n他殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁有冇她殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?? 謀殺,遇害<br />\n<br />\n帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個最多人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該用 吹風 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人最叻係吹 <br />\n<br />\n例句 <br />\n1.屌你 咩風吹你黎? 咁都見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.你吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.今晚幫我吹?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.港共吹哂風咩咩咩,大家唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15285353fd41b2a9f9faa87b9cd1bab952455dbc","tid":2037280,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:46:47.000Z","msg":"咁快有芝麻人負評"},{"pid":"3d1afd8301e7e6442c410ddc82184548eaa353ca","tid":2037280,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:50:10.000Z","msg":"之鋒IG出咗長文用吸睛呢個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f08110d0bc85ddde2130282b96394ee2e74983f","tid":2037280,"uid":46061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:52:34.000Z","msg":"仲有套路<br />\n好撚憎呢個詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfc1be21280c629604e83d56